Text: REHi Jeff How are you I havent quite melted yet but I am coming close It has been very hot here but I know I cant expect to get any sympathy from someone who lives in Texas Thank you for thinking of me in regards to Sen Schumers fundraising What is his fundraisers name I may know her or of her at least The political fundraising world is pretty small I am not sure what to make of the sunglasses comment because via email I cant tell if you were joking or serious But in either case the answer is no Anyway thanks again for thinking of me Hope all is well with you Jennie
REHi Jeff at the Four Seasons Hotel Sounds good Should there be any change and you want to reach me my cell phone is the best place Otherwise I will see you Friday Looking forward to it Jennie
REHi Jeff I hope you had a good weekend in New York and a good trip back to Texas Thank you very much for dinner the other night It was very nice to have met you Jennie
REHi Jeff I will be around the week of August st When you know what your schedule is going to be like let me know and we will make plans Where did you live in NYC Are you from NY originally
